take judicial proceedings against you. The copied @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY} will be blocked
in all following versions of XTrace.

I can send you the @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY} also via e-mail (uu-encoded or mime-encoded).

