@NODE DISTRIBUTION "1.5 Distribution"
@{b}@{u}1.5 Distribution@{uu}@{ub}

The program may be distributed and copied freely as long as the following
conditions are fulfilled :

- The sales price must not be higher than the cost of an (empty)
  disk plus a nominal copying fee plus costs for shipping. The
  total price must not be higher than DM 5.00 (or an equivalent
  in other currencies).

- All parts of the program, except the @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY}, and the docu-
  mentation must be complete. The distribution of single parts or
  incomplete subsets of the original packet is @{b}NOT ALLOWED@{ub}.

- It is @{b}NOT ALLOWED@{ub} to distribute the complete XTrace packet, single parts
  or incomplete subsets of XTrace together with other programs as packet
  without my permission.

- The @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY} may NOT BE COPIED. In case the @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY} is passed on to
  third persons @{"I" link AUTHOR } will take judicial proceedings against this
  registered person. The copied @{"keyfile" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/GLOSSARY} will be blocked in all
  following versions of XTrace.

- Archives, program and documentation may not be changed in any way.

- Reengineering the program is @{b}NOT ALLOWED@{ub}.

- Permission has been given for distribution through Aminet, Fish,
  Time, Saar AG and AmigaMagazin Networks, CDs and Disks.

For other conditions please contact the @{"author" link AUTHOR }.
@ENDNODE

@NODE ERRORREPORTS "1.6 Error-Reports"
@{b}@{u}1.6 Error-Reports@{uu}@{ub}

Please contact @{"me" link AUTHOR }, too, if you encounter bugs, in case you have
ideas for making XTrace better, or if have you comments, criticism,
contributions, questions, gifts etc.

Only send bug reports if the @{"unknown" link XTrace_Appendix.guide/KNOWNBUGS} errors are related
to XTrace and not system errors or errors from other tasks.

An error report should include the following informations:

 - exact error description

 - XTrace-version (versionsnumber, evolutionlevel, CPU-version)

 - configuration of used Amiga (CPU, memory, gfx card)

 - describe the complete working process of XTrace until the error appeared
   so that @{"I" link AUTHOR } can try to locate the error.

   If the error only occurs with one or several pictures, send these
   pictures to me (e-mail uuencoded).

   If the error only occurs with some settings or/and operator parameters,
   send these too, please.

 If I can't reproduce the error, it's hard to find it.
@ENDNODE

